message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Finally, I've been waiting here forever. My car insurance premium has increased, and I need it sorted out now!
I'm sorry to hear about the increase in your insurance premium. Let me check that for you. Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for completing security. Can you also confirm your date of birth, please?
That's all correct. To access your account, can you provide me with your first line of address and postcode?
Great, thank you. Just to finalize security, can you confirm your email address?

Thank you for completing security. I understand your concern about the increase in your premium. A possible resolution could be to review your policy and see if there are any adjustments that can be made to lower the cost. How does that sound to you?
I need it to be sorted right now. Can't you just lower my premium without all these questions?
I completely understand your urgency, Sarah. Let me check what options are available for you. Please allow me a moment to look into this for you.
Hurry up, please. This is taking too long!
I apologize for any inconvenience, Sarah. Thank you for your patience. I have found a way forward to adjust your premium. Does this work for you?
Yes, that's fine. Just get it done quickly!
I'm glad that I was able to help resolve your concern, Sarah. Your premium has been adjusted, and you should see the changes reflected shortly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you for your help
You are welcome, Sarah. If you have any more questions in the future, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
